{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbd035285-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c","identifier":"/us/usc/t13/s25"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"25"},"text":"§ 25.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Duties of supervisors, enumerators, and other employees","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd035286-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c","identifier":"/us/usc/t13/s25/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Each supervisor shall perform the duties imposed upon him by the Secretary in the enforcement of chapter 5 of this title in accordance with the Secretary’s orders and instructions.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbd035287-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c","identifier":"/us/usc/t13/s25/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Each enumerator or other employee detailed to serve as enumerator shall be charged with the collection in his subdivision of the facts and statistics called for on such schedules as the Secretary determines shall be used by him in connection with any census or survey provided for by chapter 5 of this title.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbd035288-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-31/ch1158"},"text":"Aug. 31, 1954, ch. 1158","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68/1015"},"text":"68 Stat. 1015","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/530"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–530","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-08-31"},"text":"Aug. 31, 1964","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/78/737"},"text":"78 Stat. 737","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbd035289-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idbd03528a-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Historical and Revision Notes","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Based on title 13, U.S.C., 1952 ed., §§ 122, 205, and ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1442"},"text":"section 1442 of title 42","children":[],"tail":", U.S.C., 1952 ed., The Public Health and Welfare ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1929-06-18/ch28/s5"},"text":"June 18, 1929, ch. 28, § 5","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/46/22"},"text":"46 Stat. 22","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-06-19/ch502/s2"},"text":"June 19, 1948, ch. 502, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/479"},"text":"62 Stat. 479","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-07-15/ch338"},"text":"July 15, 1949, ch. 338","children":[],"tail":", title VI, § 607, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/63/441"},"text":"63 Stat. 441","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section consolidates ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t13/s205"},"text":"section 205 of title 13","children":[],"tail":", U.S.C., 1952 ed., with that part of section 122 of such title which made such section 205 applicable to the surveys provided for by section 121 of such title (see subchapter IV of chapter 5), and with that part of subsection (b) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1442"},"text":"section 1442 of title 42","children":[],"tail":", U.S.C., 1952 ed., which made such section 205 applicable to the censuses of housing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"References to the Secretary, meaning the Secretary of Commerce, were substituted for references to the Director of the Census, to conform with 1950 Reorganization Plan No. 5, §§ 1, 2, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-05-24"},"text":"May 24, 1950","children":[],"tail":", 15 F.R. 3174, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/1263"},"text":"64 Stat. 1263","children":[],"tail":". See Revision Note to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t13/s4"},"text":"section 4 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Changes were made in phraseology and arrangement.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbd03528b-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idbd03528c-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1964—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/530"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–530","children":[],"tail":" repealed subsec. (c) which related to duties of enumerators in Bureau of the Census."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
